Message:
Oh, I know!
Do you wanna hear about
before Dezzy here got
comfortable with my head?
I was in a different place—

one that was kinda like
my hometown...

It was the total opposite of here—
completely lifeless and silent,
like the world ended
a long time ago.

I heard there were people
in the past who tried to
save that world,

but I guess it didn’t
go too well.
